**Core Skills & Technology**
Networking, VLAN, VPN, Cybersecurity, Python, PySpark, SQL, Salesforce, AWS, Linux.

**Education & Certifications**
Tung is currently pursuing a degree in Computer Networks and Data Communication at Ton Duc Thang University, expected to graduate in 2026. They hold a certification from Cisco Network Academy as an Ethical Hacker.